<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; color: #111; }
    .card { max-width: 540px; margin: 32px auto; padding: 24px; border: 1px solid #eee; border-radius: 12px; }
    h1 { color: #FF3E54; font-size: 22px; }
    .row { padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0; }
    .label { color: #666; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <h1>Booking confirmed 🎉</h1>
    <p>Hey, your rental is locked in. Here are the details:</p>
    <div class="row"><span class="label">Reference:</span> <strong>{{ reference }}</strong></div>
    <div class="row"><span class="label">Car:</span> {{ carName }}</div>
    <div class="row"><span class="label">Dates:</span> {{ start }} → {{ end }}</div>
    <div class="row"><span class="label">Total:</span> ${{ total }}</div>
    <p style="margin-top: 16px;">See you on the road.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
